      "x": 10,
      "y": 2,
      "lines": [
        "VIOLET CITY",
        "A highland town, grown up",
        "around an ancient Academy.",
        "Mind the wind."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 6,
      "y": 4,
      "lines": [
        "POKÉMON CENTER",
        "Rest your team — free",
        "for trainers."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 15,
      "y": 4,
      "lines": [
        "POKÉ MART",
        "Supplies for the climb."
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "Wind-vane flavor interaction (docs: the town's vibe).",
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 6,
      "y": 7,
      "lines": [
        "A copper wind-vane, shaped",
        "like a gust-dancer. It swings,",
        "settles north.",
        "Wind's always been good here."
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "STATUE — the founding pair; examine → the founding lore (the bond thesis, quietly in stone).",
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 13,
      "y": 18,
      "lines": [
        "THE FOUNDING PAIR — Violet's",
        "first master and their",
        "gust-dancer, caught mid-launch",
        "into the wind.",
        "",
        "The plaque is worn nearly",
        "smooth: \"Before the Academy,",
        "before the name — there was a",
        "girl who learned to read the",
        "wind, and a creature that",
        "chose to ride it with her.",
        "",
        "Everything here grew from that",
        "one understanding. Strength",
        "was never the lesson. Trust",
        "was.\""
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "NOTICE BOARD — town news + the ignored Concord flyer.",
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 17,
      "y": 18,
      "lines": [
        "VIOLET NOTICE BOARD",
        "• Gym challenge: FALKNER waits",
        "  atop the gym.",
        "• Academy open day — all are",
        "  welcome to the grounds.",
        "",
        "(A glossy CONCORD flyer is",
        "pinned in the corner. Nobody",
        "has so much as creased it.)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "CONCORD SEED — billboard (static slogan), re-homed into the square beside the statue.",
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 11,
      "y": 21,
      "lines": [
        "CONCORD billboard:",
        "\"A partner takes ten years to",
        "trust you. The Concordance",
        "takes ten minutes.\""
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "LOOKOUT — the highland payoff over the valley.",
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 2,
      "y": 27,
      "lines": [
        "THE LOOKOUT",
        "The whole valley opens below —",
        "Route 31 winding back the way",
        "you came, the lowlands hazy",
        "beyond.",
        "Up here, the wind never stops."
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "Gym guide (kept) — points the way + foreshadows the gym's wind.",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 11,
      "color": "#3a7fbe",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "GYM GUIDE: Down the lane is",
            "FALKNER's gym. The wind is the",
            "third fighter up there.",
            "Beat his trainers first —",
            "they hand out a scout report."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "THEMED NPC 1 — the Academy keeper (the old man), the lore-keeper by the statue.",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 19,
      "color": "#caa148",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "OLD MAN: This Academy's older",
            "than the cobblestones, older",
            "than the name. The town grew",
            "up around it, not the other",
            "way round.",
            "Folks forget that."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "THEMED NPC 2 — the gust-dancer kid (foreshadows the gym + the GALE ecosystem).",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 15,
      "y": 19,
      "color": "#88c0e8",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "KID: See the gust-dancers",
            "riding the updraft this",
            "morning?",
            "One day I'll read the wind",
            "like FALKNER does."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "THEMED NPC 3 — the unbothered local (the town's relaxed defiance; merges the old Concord-dismissal townsperson).",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 11,
      "y": 20,
      "color": "#a8743a",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "LOCAL: Concord folks set up",
            "their booth. We waved.",
            "Then we went back to it the",
            "way we always have.",
            "No hurry."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "CONCORD SEED — kiosk (re-homed into the square; flavor ONLY, fully ignorable, one-time set-flag). docs/concord-seed-ch1.md.",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 10,
      "y": 20,
      "color": "#7fd4e0",
      "blockedUntilFlag": "concord_kiosk_read",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "A polished kiosk hums in the",
            "square — soft light, clean",
            "lines, the CONCORD mark above.",
            "Out of place in the warm town.",
            "",
            "\"Training is a beautiful",
            "tradition — and a slow,",
            "uncertain one. Years of hoping",
            "a partner learns to trust you.",
            "The risk it never does.",
            "",
            "The CONCORDANCE offers another",
            "way: strength on the first day,",
            "loyalty without the decade of",
            "doubt. We don't ask you to earn",
            "a bond you may never live to",
            "see — we make it obsolete.",
            "",
            "The Concordance between human",
            "and mon, perfected. Ask us how.\""
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "set-flag",
          "flag": "concord_kiosk_read"
        }
      ],
      "interactAfterFlag": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "The CONCORD kiosk hums softly.",
            "\"Strength on the first day.",
            "The Concordance, perfected.",
            "Ask us how.\""
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "CONCORD SEED — rep NPC (calm true believer; warm, not a villain), re-homed into the square.",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 10,
      "y": 21,
      "color": "#bfe6ee",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "CONCORD REP: Welcome! No",
            "pressure at all. I used to",
            "train the old way too — years",
            "of waiting, hoping.",
            "CONCORD REP: We just think",
            "people deserve to skip the",
            "heartbreak. Strength, today.",
            "Have a wonderful afternoon."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "Living-world — a kid flying a kite in the square.",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 11,
      "y": 18,
      "color": "#b14e9c",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "KITE KID: Up, up — there she",
            "goes! The thermals off the",
            "Academy tower are the best in",
            "town for kites."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "Living-world — an NPC who feeds the gust-dancers wheeling over the rooftops.",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 19,
      "y": 18,
      "color": "#6c5a48",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "FEEDER: Here they come — the",
            "FLITPECK know my whistle.",
            "Wild gust-dancers, but they",
            "trust a steady hand.",
            "Everything here works that way."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "Living-world — the shopkeeper outside the Mart, local flavor.",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 17,
      "y": 6,
      "color": "#8c6240",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "SHOPKEEPER: Heading up to the",
            "gym? Pack potions. The wind",
            "up there doesn't care how",
            "ready you feel."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "Living-world — an old couple on a bench by the lookout (quiet life).",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 4,
      "y": 26,
      "color": "#9c8a78",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "OLD WOMAN: We come up here",
            "most evenings. Watch the light",
            "go off the valley.",
            "OLD MAN: Sixty years. The wind",
            "hasn't run out yet."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "Living-world — sparring students in the Academy yard (flavor).",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 3,
      "y": 24,
      "color": "#6a8f3a",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "STUDENT: Read first, THEN move.",
            "That's the whole craft. The",
            "Academy drills it into you",
            "before they let you near the",
            "gym."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "Living-world — a second student crossing to the yard.",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 4,
      "y": 25,
      "color": "#9ad470",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "STUDENT: The Concord says skip",
            "the decade. But you can't",
            "shortcut a read. You either",
            "see it coming or you don't."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_note": "DELL (kept) — the spar-able Academy student, re-homed to the yard. Existing trainer battle (GRITHOAX); one-time win flag + reward.",
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 5,
      "y": 24,
      "color": "#7c4fa8",
      "blockedUntilFlag": "violet_schoolkid_beaten",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "DELL: I study battles after",
            "class. No fancy tricks yet —",
            "just a clean read. Quiz me!"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "start-trainer-battle",
          "foeSpecies": "GRITHOAX",
          "winFlag": "violet_schoolkid_beaten",
          "reward": 400
        }
      ],
      "interactAfterFlag": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "DELL: Textbook. I'll note",
            "that down."
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
